Package: imx-kernel-api-4.9.y-imx8-sr
Architecture: arm64
Provides: imx-kernel-api
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, linux-4.9.y-imx8-sr-dev (= ${binary:Version})
Description: i.MX series kernel API
